buildCommand: pnpm --filter website run build && ROOT=$PWD; if [ -d website ]; then ROOT=$PWD; elif [ -d ../website ]; then ROOT=$(cd .. && pwd); fi; DEST=$ROOT/.vercel/output/static; mkdir -p "$DEST"; cp -R "$ROOT/website/dist"/. "$DEST"; mkdir -p "$ROOT/.vercel/output"; echo '{"version":3}' > "$ROOT/.vercel/output/config.json"
